---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy"
  description="A short operational account of analytics, request logs, and email on kotona.app."
>
  <section class="page-intro">
    <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
    <h1 class="page-title">A small site with a small data surface.</h1>

    <p class="page-copy">
      Cloudflare provides hosting and Web Analytics. The analytics beacon is
      used for aggregate traffic and performance measurement, not individual
      profiling. This site has no accounts, comments, advertising, or
      behavioural tracking.
    </p>

    <p class="page-copy">
      Cloudflare and Worker observability may process ordinary request metadata
      such as IP address, user agent, requested path, and timestamp for service
      operation, security, and abuse response.
    </p>

    <p class="page-copy">
      Using the email link creates an ordinary email interaction. The message
      and its addressing metadata are handled by the sender’s and recipient’s
      email providers and may be retained as correspondence.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
